The paper addresses the problem of image captioning, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The approach involves training a language model and using a shared latent space for the two modalities, which suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with multimodal embeddings, which is a topic that falls under multimedia (cs.MM).
